Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will avenge everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even through difficult times,\NI could carry on without giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because of one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To realize that, I need like-minded allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need the help of you all\Nwho are living in the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all share one wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... For the last 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the heir to the Daimyo \Nof the Land of the Wano...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kozuki Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to rise up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Orochi's Hunting Party!\NThe Ninja Group vs. Zoro!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorojuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with them here. You go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorojuro-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tower Climb Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorojuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a serious criminal\Nwho pointed a sword at Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you regret\Nstanding against Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorojuro! Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many ninja are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry for getting in your way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get killed,\NI wouldn't be able to face Momonosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go back to the \Nhouse in the snow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not matter\Nas long as I can hide myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna get back to the \Nguy who stole my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I will guide you to him.\NBandit's Bridge in Ringo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get it back \Nbefore the great battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel comfortable without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I made Orochi really mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hunting party's so pesky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Otoko is doing okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.81,0:07:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After such a horrible thing\Nhappened to her father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was not able to stay by her side,\Nso I am worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.67,0:08:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's with my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She should be fine, at least physically...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll avenge Tonoyasu at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish... I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...kill him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You let them get away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the ronin who attacked me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am disappointed in you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we captured a man named Trafalgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra... falgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Straw Hat,\Nhe is one of their masterminds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, now we have two heads of the intruder group\Nunder control!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world of pirates,\Nbetrayal never goes out of style!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after torturing him,\Nwe can use him in so many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the status of the capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We put it on high alert
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and stationed patrol-force samurai\Nand ninja all over the town!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until those intruders are all caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will see to it that you are well defended!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see any of these faces,\Nreport it immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are all wanted posters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep in mind that letting them walk away\Nor hiding them will be considered conspiracy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:06.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SANGORO THE SOBA COOK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should steer clear of \Nthe capital from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just the capital!\NWe're wanted across the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SHINOBU THE {\i1}KUNOICHI{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever we go,\NOrochi's assassins will be on the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our wanted posters have been spread spread\Nthroughout the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the capital isn't the only place\Nthat's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're considered diabolical outlaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in a way, our business \Nin the capital is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our objective was to find\Nsamurai with the moon tattoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all those samurai are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Behind bars now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.73,0:11:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get us out of here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:12:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After Tonoyasu gave that speech risking his own life,\NI thought they'd be considered innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Prisoners' Quarters are vast.\NI assume that about a thousand people got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, haven't they been freed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0} would say,\N"I made a mistake"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't admit that he was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now we know that they're our allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely need their help!\NWe've got to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law's crew must be in there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Shinobu-{\i1}chan{\i0},\Nwhat are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're making Sky Boats!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Boats?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Festival is approaching,\Nso they're preparing for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've lost two big figures.\NI bet they don't feel like having a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Actually, it's the opposite!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Festival in the Flower Capital\Nis an event to honor the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the festival, the better the \Nchance that your thoughts will reach the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... So it's an important \Nfestival for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw hat man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. The medicine is working.\NHe'll get better soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The medicine has worked already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Don't push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some... thing... to... eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.24,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me something to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and eat a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I want more!\N--Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you got better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopperemon-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the others are safely neutralized, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed by your skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:16:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your compliments don't \Nmake me happy, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a surge of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry to make you worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you guys got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luckily, we escaped.\N--I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before he died, a Daimyo named Yasuie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Yasuie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:17:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He drew the symbol and showed it\Nto the people in the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two lines added on the snake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the symbol's meaning\Nwas altered by those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people from the Land of Wano\Nknew what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Yasuie's last message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is very important!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to hand it to Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.98,0:17:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm counting on you!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need help, come to Amigasa Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Say hi to everyone else for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:18:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do with our polar bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your ability,\Nyou can get them out in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fool would keep all the hostages\Nin one conspicuous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put you in that jail, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have four lives now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only cut me up\Nafter you've killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the three from your own crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boss must take responsibility\Nfor his henchmen's blunder...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut both you and them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bargaining chip is your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bargain"?\NWhat do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I refuse, Trafalgar Law...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will take my life along with yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A threat from a man\Nunwilling to bet on tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is something that raises concern\Nfor my own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I'm sorry! We blew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the lives of you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a complete liberation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no problem, do you, Trafalgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever tell Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0} and the others\Nthat I got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Because of our blunder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Captain is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hang around and do nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Heart Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take our captain back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Captain's life is more important\Nthan Kin'emon's plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.41,0:21:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NYou're acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:22:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's an easy job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be over as soon as you spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His people and the Straw Hats are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to in this Land of Wano?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down Kaido, the Straw Hats and \Ntheir allies from the Land of Wano{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}make their moves for the great battle\Nand deepen their bonds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, at Onigashima, Big Mom and Kaido,\Nfinally meet each other creating a tense atmosphere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a volatile situation!\NWhat will happen to the Land of Wano?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece! "Tension Rises\Nin Onigashima! Two Emperors of the Sea Meet?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
